 inhomogeneous system consisting of a strain\nengineered one dimensional moir\\'e in bilayer graphene, finding localized\nstates near the Dirac point that arise from electron trapping in a\nsemi-classical moir\\'e potential. The semi-classical density of states of these\nlocalized states we show to be in perfect agreement with an exact quantum\nmechanical calculation of the density of states.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 27 Nov 2016 17:41:48 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 2 Dec 2016 22:08:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-08-02"}
