 rate constants are presented here. The\nkinetic isotope effects for the various cases are compared to experimental data\nas well as to expressions commonly used in astrochemical models. Both the\nrectangular barrier and the Eckart approximations lead to errors of about an\norder of magnitude. Finally, fits of the rate constants are provided as input\nfor astrochemical models.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 28 Nov 2016 15:29:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-12-01"}
